{"tid":1848892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要小心漁船d大陸漁工係香港播毒","createTime":"2020-01-28T17:10:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T03:45:58.000Z","uid":6103,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ad7a2c1f384772dcb780365f8de195bd6fa47f6d","tid":1848892,"uid":6103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T17:10:31.000Z","msg":"佢地好多都會係初5到初8，9 坐漁船返香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知海事處，漁農處會唔會查佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n亦唔知佢地夠唔夠船截住佢地<br />\n<br />\n呢堆大陸漁工好高危，隨時直入香港<br />\n係漁市場播毒，傳俾d漁車司機，再經漁車播毒到全香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fad8a052b203d7d5b2f311da548a45fda78cdbb6","tid":1848892,"uid":189650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T17:11:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"32239e1bb458c75f77b9a86520f0a9c2ab46c7c7","tid":1848892,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T17:11:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全體香港市民要求將所有口岸（包括機場、羅湖、落馬洲、深圳灣、港珠澳大橋）全面禁止來自中國大陸旅客入境香港，否則繼續三罷！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">備注：<br />\n1.）非中國大陸旅客（包括台灣）可以正常入境香港<br />\n2.）擁有香港永久性居民身分可以正常入境香港<br />\n3.）香港永久性居民及其他國藉旅客經中國大陸入境香港必須接受為期14日隔離及醫學監察</span>"},{"pid":"3fcc91d18693711a7c2e353b9d51c06f1bdfd7d6","tid":1848892,"uid":6103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T17:20:41.000Z","msg":"大家幫手推，注意下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fb4b05a316abbd3ec06ea74b3fe3b7034cb256d","tid":1848892,"uid":6103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T17:38:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f9d09b23f2fbb9d4404093a00cec18057bd020b","tid":1848892,"uid":76591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite